nounce a few compatible WPML themes.</p>\n<p>The themes are, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/striking-multiflex-ecommerce-responsive-wp-theme/128763" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Striking Multiflex</a>, <a href="https://www.pixelemu.com/themes/i/40-fashion-beauty/7-pe-beauty-center" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">PE Beauty Center</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/primetrans-logistics-wordpress-theme/14122657" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">PrimeTrans</a>, <a href="https://themeforest.net/item/agile-lightweight-blogging-and-shopping-wordpress-theme/16122474" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Agile</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Striking Multiflex</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Striking MulitFlex is a powerful and flexible wordpress theme featuring a framework that can scale for large sites and web requirements.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/striking-multiflex-ecommerce-responsive-wp-theme/128763" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Striking Multiflex</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">PE Beauty Center</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Premium WordPress theme for professions like hairdresser, massage salon, spa center, fashion stylist, manicure or even fitness gym.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://www.pixelemu.com/themes/i/40-fashion-beauty/7-pe-beauty-center" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Download PE Beauty Center</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">PrimeTrans</h2>\n<blockquote><p>PrimeTrans is Fully Responsive, Retina-Ready clean and flexible logistics WordPress Theme</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/primetrans-logistics-wordpress-theme/14122657" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase PrimeTrans</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Agile</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Agile is a clean, simple and lightweight WordPress theme suitable for Blogging and Online Shopping</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://themeforest.net/item/agile-lightweight-blogging-and-shopping-wordpress-theme/16122474" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Purchase Agile</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=uRQPbnp_FxE:yU7T2FhUXaM:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=uRQPbnp_FxE:yU7T2FhUXaM:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=uRQPbnp_FxE:yU7T2FhUXaM:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=uRQPbnp_FxE:yU7T2FhUXaM:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=uRQPbnp_FxE:yU7T2FhUXaM:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=uRQPbnp_FxE:yU7T2FhUXaM:V_sGLi