(572, 1, '2015-03-31 08:14:43', '2015-03-31 08:14:43', '[vc_row el_class="text-center" layout="wide" parallax_style="none" parallax_scroll_effect="fixed" parallax_speed="0" overlay_set="hide_overlay" overlay_opacity="50"][vc_column width="1/1"][zorka_icon_box layout_style="style1" icon="pe-7s-map-marker" icon_position="center" link="#" title="5th Floor, 209 Saint-Paul West Montreal, Canada" el_class="margin-bottom-35"][zorka_button layout_style="style1" size="button-sm" button_label="JOIN US" link="#" link_target="" el_class="margin-bottom-70"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row layout="boxed" parallax_style="none" parallax_scroll_effect="fixed" parallax_speed="0" overlay_set="hide_overlay" overlay_opacity="50"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1427790921636{border-top-width: 5px !important;border-right-width: 5px !important;border-bottom-width: 5px !important;border-left-width: 5px !important;padding-top: 50px !important;padding-right: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;border-left-color: #eeeeee !important;border-left-style: solid !important;border-right-color: #eeeeee !important;border-right-style: solid !important;border-top-color: #eeeeee !important;border-top-style: solid !important;border-bottom-color: #eeeeee !important;border-bottom-style: solid !important;}"]\n<p style="text-align: center;">If you’d like to apply, get out your resume, throw it away, and talk to us like we’re human. Send us something cool you made or a long rant on how terrible the freelancing process is right now and how, if you ruled the world, everything would be better.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ca7279;">Come help us build the future of work!</span></p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row layout="boxed" parallax_style="none" parallax_scroll_effect="fixed" parallax_speed="0" overlay_set="hide_overlay" overlay_opacity="50"][vc_column width="1/1"][zorka_heading layout_style="style2" title="POSITIONS"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="hiring-box margin-bottom-40" layout="boxed" parallax_style="none" parallax_scroll_effect="fixed" parallax_speed="0" overlay_set="hide_overlay" overlay_opacity="50"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\n<h6 style="text-align: left;">BACKEND DEVELOPER</h6>\n<p style="text-align: left;">As a Backend Developer, you will be working on our vetting and work matching system. It is a framework that directly impacts the livelihood of thousands of people.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">PHP</li>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">CakePHP</li>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">MySQL</li>\n</ul>\nFULL-TIME • MONTREAL[/vc_column_text][zorka_button layout_style="style1" size="button-sm" button_label="JOIN US" link="#" link_target=""][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\n<h6 style="text-align: left;">FRONTEND DEVELOPER/DESIGNER</h6>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Design is central to everything we do at Crew. You will be responsible for creating a delightful user experience for everyone on Crew, from seasoned freelancers to first-time members.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">HTML and CSS</li>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">LESS</li>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Javascript</li>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">PHP</li>\n</ul>\nFULL-TIME • MONTREAL[/vc_column_text][zorka_button layout_style="style1" size="button-sm" button_label="JOIN US" link="#" link_target=""][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\n<h6 style="text-align: left;">COMMUNITY AMBASSADOR</h6>\n<p style="text-align: left;">You are responsible for building Crew’s community of freelancers. Tasks include screening freelance members, introducing members to new projects, and writing member profiles. You will also be in charge of our tweets, Facebook posts, and other tools we explore to have conversations with our community.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Knowledge of design and development roles</li>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Freelance experience</li>\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Twitter/Facebook skills</li>\n</ul>\nFULL-TIME • MONTREAL[/vc_column_text][zorka_button layout_style="style1" size="button-sm" button_label="JOIN US" link="#" link_target=""][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\n<h6 style="text-align: left;">RUBY ON RAILS DEVELOPER</h6>\n<p style="text-align: left;">You will help build and scale Unsplash to tens of millions of users.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Rails</li>\n	<li>Postgres</li>\n	<li>Redis</li>\n	<li>RSpec + Capybara</li>\n	<li>Sidekiq</li>\n	<li>Elasticsearch</li>\n</ul>\nFULL-TIME • REMOTE[/vc_column_text][zorka_button layout_style="style1" size="button-sm" button_label="JOIN US" link="#" link_target=""][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\n<h6 style="text-align: left;">HAPPINESS CONCIERGE</h6>\n<p style="text-align: left;">You will help our members have a memorable experience using Crew. Treating people right is just as much a part of our product as any webpage we design or code that we write. You’re the right fit for this position if:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Your inbox is zero</li>\n	<li>You know how to write concise, actionable emails</li>\n	<li>You have experience estimating design/development projects</li>\n	<li>You have sales experience</li>\n</ul>\nFULL-TIME • REMOTE[/vc_column_text][zorka_button layout_style="style1" size="button-sm" button_label="JOIN US" link="#" link_target=""][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\n<h6 style="text-align: left;">HEAD OF GROWTH</h6>\n<p style="text-align: left;">You will be on the lookout for new and experimental ways we can grow Crew.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Growth marketing</li>\n	<li>Ads (Twitter, Facebook, Google, LinkedIn)</li>\n	<li>Community-building</li>\n	<li>Product management</li>\n</ul>\nFULL-TIME • REMOTE[/vc_column_text][zorka_button layout_style="style1" size="button-sm" button_label="JOIN US" link="#" link_target=""][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Hiring', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hiring', '', '', '2015-03-31 08:14:43', '2015-03-31 08:14:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/theface/?page_id=572', 0, 'page', '', 0),
